title: Tasty Cream Cheese Chicken Roll Recipe
content:
Cream Cheese Chicken Roll-Ups Recipe taste so delicious and is pretty easy to make as well. This makes a great party snack or appetizer as well.

 

Cream Cheese Chicken Roll-Ups Recipe

Prep time: 10 mins

Total time: 10 mins

 

Cream Cheese Chicken Roll-Ups Recipe taste so delicious and is pretty easy to make as well. This makes a great party snack or appetizer as well.

Author: Aarthi

Recipe type: Main

Cuisine: American

Serves: 2 servings

 

Ingredients

Tortilla or Leftover Roti - 2

Cream Cheese - ½ cup

Salt to taste

Pepper to taste

Onion - ¼ cup chopped finely

Capsicum - ¼ cup chopped finely

Leftover Cooked Chicken - 2 cups shredded

Olives - 3 tablespoons

 

Instructions

Mix all ingredients except roti. Spread over tortilla or roti.

Roll it tight.

Cut it into pieces and serve it.
